commitResults.messageBody:
Initially, an error in the JSON file caused an empty Addressbook to be loaded.
This can cause the user to be confused as to what can be done, thus we made a sample data be loaded
when a bug occurred.

This fixes the AB3 requirement where a sample addressbook should be loaded when the
save file is corrupted
